<!-- POPUP PAGAMENTO COM PIX -->
<section id="sectionPix" class="overflow-y-auto hidden  max-w-screen-md w-full max-h-screen h-full border shadow-lg fixed md:top-1/2 top-0 md:left-1/2 left-0 p-10 bg-gradient-to-r bg-white md:transform md:-translate-x-1/2 md:-translate-y-1/2 space-y-4">
    <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 pt-5">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="30" height="30" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-cart-check-fill text-c1" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path d="M.5 1a.5.5 0 0 0 0 1h1.11l.401 1.607 1.498 7.985A.5.5 0 0 0 4 12h1a2 2 0 1 0 0 4 2 2 0 0 0 0-4h7a2 2 0 1 0 0 4 2 2 0 0 0 0-4h1a.5.5 0 0 0 .491-.408l1.5-8A.5.5 0 0 0 14.5 3H2.89l-.405-1.621A.5.5 0 0 0 2 1zM6 14a1 1 0 1 1-2 0 1 1 0 0 1 2 0m7 0a1 1 0 1 1-2 0 1 1 0 0 1 2 0m-1.646-7.646-3 3a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-1.5-1.5a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708L8 8.293l2.646-2.647a.5.5 0 0 1 .708.708"/>
        </svg>
        <h2 class="text-gray-700">Pague com QR Code ou PIX copiar e colar!</h2>
    </div>
    <h2>Após a confirmação do pagamento, entraremos em contato para agendar a entrega. Por favor, <b>verifique se o seu número de contato está correto.</b> <%= typeof  endereco != "undefined" &&  endereco.telefone ? endereco.telefone :  'Não cadastrado'   %> </h2>

    <div class="progress-bar relative duration-200">
        <p id="ContadorTempo" class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2">3:00</p>
    </div>

    <button id="fecharSectionPix" class="absolute top-2 right-3">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="25" height="25" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-x-lg text-red-500" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
            <path d="M2.146 2.854a.5.5 0 1 1 .708-.708L8 7.293l5.146-5.147a.5.5 0 0 1 .708.708L8.707 8l5.147 5.146a.5.5 0 0 1-.708.708L8 8.707l-5.146 5.147a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L7.293 8z"/>
        </svg>
    </button>

    <!-- IMAGEM QRCODE -->
    <div class="p-1 pl-4">
        <span>Valor a pagar: </span> <span id="valorPix" class="font-semibold text-2xl text-gray-700">R$ <%= stringParaReal(carrinhoProcessado.total) %></span>
    </div>
    <img src="" alt=""  id="qrCode" class="m-auto p-1 bg-white drop-shadow-lg rounded-lg ticket__qrcode-canva--desktop max-w-[90%] border aspect-square">

    <div class="space-y-2">
        <button id="btnConfirmarPagamento"  class="hidden bg-green-500 duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:drop-shadow-lg font-semibold text-white rounded-md items-center justify-center space-x-2 px-4 py-2 m-auto">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="25" height="25" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-check-circle-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                <path d="M16 8A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0m-3.97-3.03a.75.75 0 0 0-1.08.022L7.477 9.417 5.384 7.323a.75.75 0 0 0-1.06 1.06L6.97 11.03a.75.75 0 0 0 1.079-.02l3.992-4.99a.75.75 0 0 0-.01-1.05z"/>
            </svg>
            <p>CONFIRMAR PAGAMENTO</p>
        </button>
        <button chaveCopiarColar="" id="btnCopiarPix"  class="bg-c1 duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:drop-shadow-lg font-semibold text-white rounded-md  w-52 flex items-center justify-center space-x-2 px-4 py-2 m-auto">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-clipboard" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                <path d="M4 1.5H3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2V14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h10a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V3.5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-1v1h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1V14a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H3a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V3.5a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h1z"/>
                <path d="M9.5 1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v1a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-3a.5.5 0 0 1-.5-.5v-1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5zm-3-1A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 5 1.5v1A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 6.5 4h3A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 11 2.5v-1A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 9.5 0z"/>
            </svg>
            <p >COPIAR PIX</p>
        </button>
    </div>

</section>